IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. TRANSFER.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

01 WS-CMDLINE      PIC X(100).

01 WS-FROM-STR     PIC X(30).
01 WS-TO-STR       PIC X(30).
01 WS-AMT-STR      PIC X(30).

01 WS-FROM-BAL     PIC 9(13)V99 VALUE 0.
01 WS-TO-BAL       PIC 9(13)V99 VALUE 0.
01 WS-AMOUNT       PIC 9(13)V99 VALUE 0.

01 WS-ARG-COUNT    PIC 9 VALUE 0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.

    ACCEPT WS-CMDLINE FROM COMMAND-LINE

    UNSTRING WS-CMDLINE DELIMITED BY SPACE
        INTO WS-FROM-STR WS-TO-STR WS-AMT-STR
        TALLYING WS-ARG-COUNT

    IF WS-ARG-COUNT < 3
        DISPLAY "INVALID"
        STOP RUN
    END-IF

    COMPUTE WS-FROM-BAL = FUNCTION NUMVAL(WS-FROM-STR)
    COMPUTE WS-TO-BAL   = FUNCTION NUMVAL(WS-TO-STR)
    COMPUTE WS-AMOUNT   = FUNCTION NUMVAL(WS-AMT-STR)

    IF WS-AMOUNT <= 0
        DISPLAY "INVALID"
        STOP RUN
    END-IF

    IF WS-AMOUNT > WS-FROM-BAL
        DISPLAY "FAILED"
    ELSE
        SUBTRACT WS-AMOUNT FROM WS-FROM-BAL
        ADD WS-AMOUNT TO WS-TO-BAL
        DISPLAY WS-FROM-BAL " " WS-TO-BAL
    END-IF

    STOP RUN.

